          News file for libvirt-java
	  --------------------------
Jul 29 2009:
Release of 0.3.0:
  - refactored the code to use jna (https://jna.dev.java.net/)
  
Aug  8 2008:
Release of 0.2.1:
  - clean up leaks, refactoring of JNI bindings
  - extend to support all storage APIs from 0.4.1

18 Jul 2008:
Release of 0.2.0:
  - first stable API release
  - large refactoring of JNI and classes

1 Jul 2008:
Release of 0.1.1:
  - fix some of the portability problems
  - add authentication support


